- Add a LVM Partition

    fdisk /dev/sdc

- Create physical volume

    # pvcreate /dev/sdc1

- Add the disk to the VG

    #  vgextend vg /dev/sdc1

- Increase size of LV

    #  lvextend -L+284GB /dev/pv/mysql

- Resize partition

    # #  xfs_growfs /dev/mapper/pv-mysql
